{
  "name": "Error",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>Errors</strong> 对象的 <strong>Item</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>Error</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p>返回 <strong>Error</strong> 对象后，可结合使用 <strong>Value</strong> 和 <strong>Errors</strong>属性检查某个特定错误检查选项是否已启用。</p>\n<p>不要将 <strong>Error</strong> 对象与 JavaScript 的错误处理功能混淆。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例中，在引用空单元格的单元格 A1 中创建一个公式，然后使用 Item(index)（其中 index 用于标识错误类型）显示描述错误情况的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> rngFormula = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>)\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Place a formula referencing empty cells.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=A2+A3&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorCheckingOptions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">EmptyCellReferences</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Perform check to see if EmptyCellReferences check is on.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (rngFormula.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEmptyCellReferences).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The empty cell references error checking feature is enabled.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The empty cell references error checking feature is not on.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例禁用单元格 C1 的错误检查选项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlTextDate).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ignore</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表区域的电子表格错误。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Ignore",
      "summary": "<p>引用 <strong>ErrorCheckingOptions</strong>对象可查看与错误检查选项相关联的索引值列表。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>允许用户设置或返回某一区域的错误检查选项的状态。如果该值为 <strong>False</strong>，则某一区域的错误检查选项可用。如果该值为 <strong>True</strong>，则禁用某一区域的错误检查选项。<strong>Boolean</strong>类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为检查空单元格引用而禁用单元格 A1 中的忽略标记。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//Determine if empty cell references error checking is on, if not turn it on.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEmptyCellReferences).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ignore</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEmptyCellReferences).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ignore</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Empty cell references error checking has been enabled for cell A1.&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Empty cell references error checking is already enabled for cell A1.&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例禁用单元格 B1 的错误检查选项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEmptyCellReferences).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Ignore</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Value",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Boolean</strong> 值，它指明是否符合所有的有效性验证条件（即，该区域是否包含有效数据）。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例将一个数字作为文本放在单元格 C1 中，然后当单元格 C1 的值包含文本格式的数字时通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;&#x27;2&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;C1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlNumberAsText).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;单元格C1有个数字作为文本&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;单元格C1有个数字&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 Error 对象的 Value 属性值。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Select</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Errors</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(xlEmptyCellReferences).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": []
}